title: Luxembourg Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Luxembourg decreased to 3465 in October from 3572 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Luxembourg averaged 3420.02  from 1981 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6419  in April of 2008 and a record low of 1166  in August of 1981. This page provides - Luxembourg Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: STATEC, Luxembourg
